Package com.barchart.feed.ddf.message.api

          Description

Interface Summary
DDF_BaseMessage base type for all ddf/xml messasges; includes: link control, market data, url lookup.
DDF_ControlBase base type for ddf feed control messages.
DDF_ControlResponse represents ddf feed server response message.
DDF_ControlTimestamp represents ddf feed server time stamp or heart beat message.
DDF_MarketBase Base type for ddf feed market data messages.
DDF_MarketBook represents ddf feed market depth snapshot.
DDF_MarketBookTop represents ddf feed top of market depth a.k.a bid/ask
DDF_MarketCondition represents ddf feed market condition.
DDF_MarketCuvol represents ddf feed market cumulative volume snapshot.
DDF_MarketParameter represents ddf feed market parameter message; carries additional price or size value, depending on parameter type;.
DDF_MarketQuote represents xml "market quote"; a collection of sessions.
DDF_MarketSession represents xml session; "extended snapshot info; part of quote".
DDF_MarketSnapshot ddf feed market snapshot messages; "reduced session info".
DDF_MarketTrade represents ddf feed market trade message.
DDF_MessageVisitor<Result,Param> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visitor_pattern
